result.name: Sun Kwong Nam Cafe

reviews.text: Average freshness and taste. 10% service /tips charge is not typical in small restaurants like this. I was caught by surprise as the extra charge was never mentioned in the menu or posted anywhere in the window posters, customers are told afterward at the cashier.
Great food and good prices. Sweet and sour pork in particular was fantastic!
食物尚好，但茶餐廳收加一，未能接受。
七點左右睇戲前路過找晚飯地方，看到評分有四星，在這不太旺的街也有很多食客（九成滿），就決定試試。原來這是一家老餐廳，很多「舊西餐」菜式。餐牌上介紹「鎮店五寶」，點了海南雞飯和咖哩牛腩飯。沒有失望！當然不是超級水準，但性價比極高，$55each。味道濃郁，咖哩椰香重不太辣，雞件滑嫩有啫哩。很久沒有吃完大碟飯仍有意猶未盡的感覺，再來一碗吧！

只有懷念，對品質絕無懸念！
再疊上加一服務費…

reviews.text: Average freshness and taste. 10% service /tips charge is not typical in small restaurants like this. I was caught by surprise as the extra charge was never mentioned in the menu or posted anywhere in the window posters, customers are told afterward at the cashier.
Not good, not bad, just an ordinary tea restaurant in mongkok.
Food ok. Price is ok. Open till late.
Set dinner is great and reasonable price. Food are great and are many choices. Love the chicken, sweet and sour pork ribs most.
portions are so big, I can't eat all that.

result.name: 新廣南餐室

reviews.text: 這間新廣南餐室的食物份量很多又好吃，價錢又不貴，值得常常去光顧。
早餐不過不失，但有麥皮加分，店內是舊式氣氛
一間感覺 舒適的古舊餐廳，如果不是繁忙時段更覺悠閒。馬來風味的食堂。服務員的質素一般。
幾抵食,重點係坐得舒服
茶餐廳格局，午餐和下午茶竟然要加一！
